<br>
Evil is a label our enemies apply to us. <br>
<br>
It dehumanizes us in their eyes and conscience, making it easier for them to commit acts against us they would never think of commiting upon their neighbor.<br>
<br>
I do not consider myself evil. I am a knight of Innoruuk, anointed by his priests and warranted by my queen to do battle with our enemies. <br>
<br>
When not under orders, I wander. Where I see injustice, I make it right.  <br>
<br>
More often than not, I see those of  the light races preying upon the weaker of thier own. When I come to the aid of these oppressed ones, I am a missionary of the freedom Innoruuk gives those who worship him. Unhindered by dogma, graced by my Gods with free will.<br>
<br>
At home, I am a protector of my people and a mitigator of the Queens justice.<br>
<br>
&lt;ooc&gt;<br>
<br>
Gee! Kinda makes me sound like one of the good guys.<br>
<br>
